    "comp_side_by_side_t7QNiP": {
      "type": "comp-side-by-side",
      "blocks": {
        "column_CnbnKW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is Reviv?",
            "text": "<p>Reviv is a flat-plane, non-locking jaw-supportive oral appliance designed for adult sleep use. Its design maintains stable vertical jaw height without locking the bite — allowing natural jaw micro-movement during sleep rather than holding the jaw in a fixed position overnight.</p><p>Many users find consistent nightly use gradually reduces morning jaw tightness and clenching sensation over weeks to months. Unlike standard guards that replicate and lock the bite, Reviv's flat-plane design allows natural jaw movement — which is the core mechanical difference.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_73.webp",
            "layout": "column-reverse"
          }
        },
        "column_tfXFbt": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is Myobrace?",
            "text": "<p>Myobrace is a <strong>myofunctional orthodontic system</strong>, largely used in children (ages 3–15), but also available for adults. It’s less about brute force and more about <strong>habit correction</strong> which encourages nasal breathing, proper tongue posture, correct swallowing, and lip seal.</p><p>The Myobrace journey typically involves a series of appliances (stages), combined with daily “Myobrace Activities” such as breathing, tongue, cheek, and lip exercises that reinforce the habits you’re reshaping.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/guard_myobrace.webp",
            "layout": "column-reverse"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "column_CnbnKW",
        "column_tfXFbt"
      ],
      "name": "Comparison Side By Side",
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-309f11fb-a7c3-4ae0-a1b0-473a4f43ce02",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
