        "text_XmEx7E": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>Myobrace is delivered through a dentist and usually costs $1000-4000.  Reviv appliances typically cost &lt;$100 and no dentist is needed.</li><li>Reviv is designed for adult sleep use and jaw mechanical support during sleep — a different purpose from Myobrace's orthodontic and habit-correction focus.</li><li>Reviv uses a flat-plane, non-locking design that avoids fixing the bite position overnight — meaningful change in jaw comfort takes consistent nightly use over months.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
